title: CONS Project London : Cons Street
description:
Cons Ambassadors Jerome Campbell and Harry Lintell (alongside flow riders Matlock Bennet Jones and Jamie Platt) spent an afternoon skating the bespoke skate space 'Cons Street' housed within CONS Project London.

Find out more about the space here http://conversecons.com/ldn

Music:
Dark City “The Boardwalk”
